These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea
2 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon
House: art-deco, palace
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing backgammon is the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |
| Beverage      | tea     | hot-chocolate |
| Game   | backgammon | scrabble      |
| House         | palace    | art-deco      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, singing
There are 2 different favourite colors: amber, black
2 different games are played: monopoly, snooker
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
2. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |
| Hobby         | singing      | magic-tricks |
| Color   | black | amber    |
| Game           | snooker         | monopoly         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, camping
2 different pets are kept: mouse, pony
There 2 different types of food: onion, nectarine
1. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2      |
| Hobby         | hiking | camping |
| Pet         | pony       | mouse       |
| Food   | nectarine       | onion         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-4::.
