The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, gardening
There 2 different types of food: asparagus, raspberry
1. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |
| Music-Genre    | rock    | salsa     |
| Hobby       | camping    | gardening |
| Food   | asparagus | raspberry    |

