.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-5::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, fantasy
2 different games are played: billiard, snooker
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike
1. the person playing snooker is the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |      2      |
| Movie-Genre       | fantasy | comedy |
| Game         | billiard      | snooker  |
| Transport   | motorbike | quad-bike   |

