House: futuristic, tower
1. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the tower house is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | zombie   |
| Pet   | hedgehog          | ferret   |
| House         | futuristic     | tower |

 